Winbdlord/Termitron:

Two McGowan's blast hit Windlord and them hit in Windlord's shoulder. 
The pain was high, Windlord felt weakest every second. He saw Depp 
went towards him and aimed agaisnt his stomach, he covered it with a 
wing while he moved to a side. The Spear hit Widnlord's Wing in that 
way that it inserted in Windlord's wing, he couldn't fly and neither 
it couldn't use his feather missile, at least not with that wing. 
Windlord shot two feather missile, with one wing, one against McGowan 
and other to Depp.

Termitron had a bad while with his enemies. he had received 1 shot 
from Barrymore, one from Alba, one of Stiller's arrows hit him in one 
of his legs, he had the good idea to land (that let him avoid Lee's 
fireball). He fired 5 times against Barrymore, 5 to Alba, 5 to Lee, 5 
to Stiller, and 5 against Depp.

After that he fell on his back. He didn't move.
